name: PUNKY
description: PUNKY is an AI-powered Discord Moderator designed to enhance Web3 communities through machine learning and seamless automation. It provides community managers with tools to automate tasks and improve engagement, offering features such as easy setup, AI ticket systems, moderation, support, growth strategies, a task system, and bot customization. PUNKY aims to streamline community management, allowing users to focus on product development while ensuring a secure and engaging environment.
